subtask_description: Place the oscilloscope probe set with id 'oscilloscope_probe_set_1' onto the 'rack_mounted_signal_analyzer_1'.
Turn on the dual-arm magnifying lamp that is uniquely located on the steel workbench.
Find the heaviest, metal object on the steel workbench and place it in the storage component shelves.
Locate the only paper item with coffee stains in the main workbench area and move it to the filter simulation station.
